OL,3,CPolice investigating suspected murder
OL,4,Cof Middlesbrough teen move search to
OL,5,CLeeds
OL,7,FPolice investigating the disappearance
OL,8,Fand suspected murder of 17-year-old
OL,9,FDonna Keogh from Middlesbrough say
OL,10,Fthey have moved their investigation to
OL,11,FLeeds.
OL,13,FCleveland Police officers say they are
OL,14,F"determined" to find out what happened
OL,15,Fto the teen and are pursuing fresh
OL,16,Flines of enquiry in the Chapeltown
OL,17,Farea of the city.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
