CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice investigating suspected murder
OL,4,Cof Middlesbrough teen move search to
OL,5,CLeeds
OL,7,FDonna Keogh went missing from
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough in April 1998. Her body
OL,9,Fwas never found and officers
OL,10,F"strongly" suspect that she was
OL,11,Fmurdered shortly after she disappeared.
OL,13,FThe 17-year-old was last seen on
OL,14,FTuesday 28 April 1998 in Bow Street,
OL,15,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
