PN,42704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice investigating suspected murder
OL,4,Cof Middlesbrough teen move search to
OL,5,CLeeds
OL,7,FIn 2018, crime scene investigators,
OL,8,Fforensics officers, police, and
OL,9,Flandscapers descended on a site in
OL,10,FSaltersgill to carry out excavation
OL,11,Fworks in the hope of finding Donna's
OL,12,Fremains.
OL,14,FDonna's father Brian Keogh recently
OL,15,Fpassed away without ever learning what
OL,16,Fhad happened to his daughter. Officers
OL,17,Fsaid this "caused profound distress to
OL,18,Fthe family".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
